name: T-Bone
description:
T-Bone Duplexus is a retired
professional alligator wrestler.
He's not very good at chess.

name: Terrence
description:
Terrence just learned
how the pieces move.
Now he wants blood.

name: Nacho
description:
Nacho is a feline grandmaster.
If he tries to eat your head,
do not let him.

name: Marco
description:
They never asked Marco
to star in a video game.
He's not happy about it.

name: Ghost
description:
Ghost was kidnapped as a child
and raised by intermediates.

name: Greta
description:
Greta was once a queen herself.
Now she lives in the woods
and plays chess with squirrels.

name: Maia
description:
Maia was a famous author
before she became a model
for Elle c0.

name: Gerard
description:
Gerard brought a sword to a chess match.
And he swings it hard.

name: Bionica
description:
Bionica was programmed
with a full range of emotions.
But she prefers contempt.

name: Mitsoko
description:
Mitsoko, like most women in anime,
is an inexplicably powerful warrior.

name: Spectre
description:
Spectre may strike without warning.
You have been warned.

name: Aurora
description:
They say Aurora can see the future.
She says she can see your defeat.

name: Null-Zo
description:
Null-Zo will not rest
until he has defeated you.
Then he will rest.

name: Eliza
description:
Eliza plays masterfully.
Some say she's a machine.
They're right.

name: ThinMan
description:
ThinMan is not your friend.
It's why he's pointing
a laser gun at your face.

name: Listress
description:
You are a wretched, pitiful worm.
Listress will not be merciful.
You may still beg.
